Global Plastic E-Scrap Recycling Service Market Insights
Plastic E-Scrap Recycling Service Market size was valued at USD 3.12 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.98 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.6% from 2024 to 2030.

Plastic E-Scrap Recycling Service Market Overview
The global plastic e-scrap recycling service market has been experiencing significant growth, reaching a market value of approximately USD 12.5 billion in 2024. This growth is fueled by the increasing volume of electronic waste and the rising environmental concerns associated with improper disposal of e-waste. The market is expected to continue expanding at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 8.1% during the forecast period (2025–2030). The growing demand for sustainable waste management solutions and the technological advancements in recycling processes contribute to this upward trend. The market is further supported by stricter government regulations regarding e-waste disposal, making recycling an essential practice across industries.

